uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1184f7d3379ea89b3b1c56add9a8365ec0753d17","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:51:03.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"79306466cf355071ab928325621b745124e091ff","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8256f80cfd1cedcdd51e70f163477ca4da12111e","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T14:32:44.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"01f3b6c619328b7239e34ecb1ee67396e2cca90c","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"a6258b2947ab624e7687b4d9eccf20e0afe47388","tid":2345411,"uid":301952,"like":26,"dislike":5,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"其實南洋華僑出過好多帝皇級人物<br />\n鄭信<br />\n吳芳伯<br />\n汶萊皇室都有華人共同開國<br />\n<br />\n睇完華僑史，福建人真係好顛，航海技術遠超想像"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"其實blog主就係話Rizal由頭到尾都冇當過自己係華人。人都死咗百幾年，嗰班三五識七嘅福建佬走嚟認親認戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n南中國海啲人由遠古開始已經走嚟走去，叫做Nusantao Network，嗰時「中華」連精蟲都未有，更莫講「華人」呢個身份。<br />\n<br />\n你講嗰幾位，都算係呢個海洋文化嘅延續。而佢哋當中，羅芳伯尚可能有「華人」認同，但其他幾位斷估都冇當過自己係咩「華人」。事實上，呢班閩粵人去印支、婆羅州可能仲適應過去京津，稱王稱帝又有乜奇。<br />\n<br />\n所以糾結華唔華人都冇乜意思，你將佢哋睇成係南中國海一部交流史會豁然開朗。"},{"pid":"2b505e943d9cfa3153869ba5076e251d3f5e258a","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T16:35:35.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"974641477f858bd668eead73bd040834ffc80b62","tid":2345411,"uid":276716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a4b743ee94cabfa9abe3e9df93353b403740e93","tid":2